Iris 0.87, Copyright (C) 2003 - 2006 Iris Team
______________________________________________

Iris is a free 3D Client for the popular Massive Multiplayer Role Playing Game Ultima Online. The current Iris version works with the Ultima Online expansions Third Dawn, Age of Shadows, Samurai Empire and Mondain's Legacy!


Iris Installation (Step 1-4):
_____________________________

1. All you need is a legal copy of Ultima Online.

   Supported Ultima Online expansions:
	- Third Dawn
	- Age of Shadows
	- Samurai Empire and Gold Trial  (SE == Gold)
	- Mondain's Legacy

   Get a free Ultima Online Mondain's Legacy :
   ___________________________________________
   http://largedownloads.ea.com/pub/uo/uoml_setup.exe


   Or free Ultima Online Gold Trial :
   __________________________________
   http://www.gamespot.com/promos/ultimaonline/index.html
   http://www.fileplanet.com/150525/150000/fileinfo/Ultima-Online-Gold-15-day-Trial

2. Install and run Ultima Online and patch it to the newest Version.

3. Install Iris.

4. Please start IrisConfig.exe or edit xml/config.xml before starting Iris !!!

Remember:
_________
- If you update/patch UO-Third Dawn, AoS, SE, Gold or ML select "Age of Shadows (AoS)" in Config!

- If you don't update/patch UO-Third Dawn for any reason select "Third Dawn" in Configtool !


Linux compilation:
__________________
aclocal
autoconf
automake -a
./configure
make


Interface:
__________
Left-Shift + Hold Right Mouse Button == Rotate and Zoom

Right-Shift + Hold Right Mouse Button == Rotate and Change Angle

Mouse wheel also controls zoom

Right Mouse Button closes Gumps

Left Mouse Button is for everything else


Option Menu:
____________
Click on the Options Menu on the Paperdoll for Camera handling.


